{
  "stem": "9168.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then we got to New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had a German girl on board that ship, who learned that I had reported the Nuremberg war trials.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was adamant that it was all propaganda by the United States and Allied countries-- all propaganda, every bit of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was not-- she was a young woman who might have been in her 30s, you know, at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that was my first encounter with Holocaust denial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I got to New York, and you know, from that point on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my older son-- our older son, was born in New York.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was there, waiting for my husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he arrived a couple months-- I was there with friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I, I did have a period of time in New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, when he arrived, we went back to Detroit, to my mother's home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was in the military.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He would be awaiting his next military assignment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he managed to have it be in New York-- I mean, in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, we were not in Detroit very long when he, he went-- we went to Lansing, Michigan shortly after our arrival, where he entered Michigan State College for some kind of a military course.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And while we were in Lansing, I worked for the Bar Association, the State Bar Association, not as a court reporter, but in their office.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there for not a long period of time-- '48?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to check my notes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I traveled-- we traveled every year after that, going from one military base to another for his assignment.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
